data.description: Welcome to your dream home in the most desirable neighborhood in Palm Beach County. Golf club without memberships. A+ rated schools. This spacious and elegant home features 3 bedrooms, 2.5 bathrooms, a modern kitchen, a cozy living room, a formal dining room, and a beautiful backyard with your own private oasis pool. You'll love the modern kitchen, the cozy living room, and the master suite with breathtaking views. Winston Trials Community is a gated community with a golf course, a pool, a gym, and a tennis court. Enjoy the friendly and active lifestyle of the neighborhood, as well as the security and privacy of the community. This home is located at walking distance to schools, shopping, dining, and entertainment. Don't miss this opportunity to own this amazing home in the Gold Communit
